    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a superb balance of performance and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the lightest signs of careful road use consistent with its age, while the alloy wheels remain free of major scuffs. Inside, you'll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the upholstery remains firm and supportive, and every electronic feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced at regular intervals, resulting in a smooth, quiet idle and responsive acceleration that makes every commute a pleasure. With a documented service history and a recent fluid flush, this is a turn-key opportunity for a discerning buyer who values a well-cared-for machine that is ready for the road ahead.",
